{"tid":1713181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門行政長官崔世安：政府聆聽民意後撤回改變非壞事","createTime":"2019-11-12T16:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:43:15.000Z","uid":22609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"755251ec4e1dc7b6f672a7628915e4a4080e1633","tid":1713181,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"(澳門電台消息) 行政長官崔世安在總結 10年施政工作記者會上表示，在他任內撤回高官離職補償法案及 600億元 (與設立投資發展基金股份有限公司相關) 的法案，對他來說不是遺憾，而是在 10年施政中吸收了經驗，需要聆聽及尊重民意。 崔世安稱，撤回高官離職補償法案的重要思想原則，是不想社會分裂，亦聽到社會有批評的聲音，因此認為不是好時機。至於撤回 600億元的法案，是政府認為要作更多解說和公眾諮詢，當社會未完全明白時，作為負責任政府，有需要讓市民明白。崔世安又以修改道路交通法的 &ldquo;牛肉乾事件&rdquo;及火葬場選址為例，指出政府在聆聽民意後改變意見，並非壞事，尊重民意是必需的。 (鄺惠敏 黃偉鴻)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyberctm.com/zh_TW/news/detail/2499491#.Xcrdtrp-WEc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cyberctm.com%2Fzh_TW%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2499491%23.Xcrdtrp-WEc&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOgu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=41859d06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cyberctm.com/zh_TW/news/detail/2499491#.Xcrdtrp-WEc</a>"},{"pid":"74a8a436452531efb85dfd4e1f215599ec3aa591","tid":1713181,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"吹屎眼"},{"pid":"d38d06c73863be5ee8bb034f92f42cdb0315296b","tid":1713181,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a8a436452531efb85dfd4e1f215599ec3aa591","tid":1713181,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:31:17.000Z","msg":"吹屎眼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"香港都有柒婆"},{"pid":"db09b573206602c7c3cae1f2b6dfc0ea530d0d92","tid":1713181,"uid":289933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"串到林奠一棟都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd1bf154885465a00bcb1419142de82ecfe0822","tid":1713181,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"乜仲未換咩?"}]}